%25AE%25A4%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25AC%258A%2F&h=4c7ad938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%BB%A3%E6%94%B6%E6%9C%83%E8%B2%BB-%E5%81%9C-%E7%AE%A1%E6%95%B8-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AC%8A/</a>"},{"pid":"e10aff6bfeeb140d4cbe31bd5978ebe9b5b21111","tid":2510283,"uid":312744,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"香港大學教務長曾詠詩今日（30 日）向全體學生發信，宣布停止為港大學生會代收會費、不再向學生會提供財務管理服務，同時會對學生會正使用的辦公室及設施「執行管理權力」（enforce our management rights），意味有可能收回港大學生會會室等設施使用權。<br />\n<br />\n信件語言為英文，指港大學生會是《社團條例》下註冊的獨立組織，為了糾正大學與學生會之間、針對法律責任問題的「長期矛盾」（protracted ambivalence），大學早前檢討向學生會提供的服務及安排，以作出「合適的風險管理」（appropriate risk management）。<br />\n<br />\n曾詠詩表示，大學決定停止為學生會代收會費、停止財務管理服務，並對學生會使用的辦公室「執行管理權力」，強調這些措施不會影響大學對支持課外活動、促進正面學習環境的承諾。"},{"pid":"2a6ffcdb95e67af03abc298efde84d33f805fb04","tid":2510283,"uid":78039,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"禮崩樂壞"},{"pid":"e9b4d21e8dafb4ac1b45a3965bdcfcc56b7a1a2f","tid":2510283,"uid":3241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"改設党委學生支部批鬥老師未"},{"pid":"2ffb4e9c0333213ba2a84d272f207c4214b0ee4a","tid":2510283,"uid":259901,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"全力支持XGDX完善学生会制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9a3227e88eeb00792c081c5787f312f2a2544e","tid":2510283,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"XGU"},{"pid":"2aef8537cb3daa9c013272933d6b002182dec1f9","tid":2510283,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"714b4b5beb0